skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: extraordinary mindset
des: This app is associated with a personal growth, self-help podcast called Ordinary People Doing Extraordinary Things, helping you live an extraordinary life with inspirational stories, mindset education, plus actionable steps, assignments and tools to help you connect better to yourself and others. You can use this app to search for and listen to specific content or simply play the latest podcast and more.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
